About Us OPEN Monday-Friday 11am-2:30am Saturday & Sunday 8am-2:30am Breakfast Served Saturday & Sunday at 8am Kitchen Opens 11am Weekdays 8am Saturday & Sunday Salty Jims is your local "dive bar" where friends come to unwind at the end of a work day, shoot pool, celebrate special occasions and of course, a little Karaoke every once in a while. We offer you our outdoor tiki bar hut, free pool hall tables for paying customers and some darned good food. Enjoy "live music" weekly on our outside patio, eat great food and make more friends. Better than Bar Food! We put together a menu of local favorites for you to enjoy once the munchies kick in!  Some items you expect like great burgers and delicious wings and a few items that our chef wanted to share with you. ​ Let us know what you think! ​ BREAKFAST - SATURDAY AND SUNDAY ONLY Starting at 8am.
